---
// Memories section component
---

<section class="testimonial" id="memories">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonial-content">
      <div class="testimonial-image">
        <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4c7a9c_6dc2372241a54033b682aaa5057503ea~mv2.png" alt="Class of 1996 memories" />
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-text">
        <blockquote>
          "High school was such a special time in our lives. I remember the pep rallies, the football games, the prom, and all the friendships we made. Thirty years later, I still think about those days and wonder what everyone is up to. This reunion is going to be amazing - I can't wait to see everyone and catch up on all the stories we've missed. It's incredible to think about how much we've all grown and changed, but I know when we get together, it'll feel like no time has passed at all."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <span class="author-name">Sarah Johnson, Class of '96</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .testimonial-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .testimonial-image {
    border-radius: 15px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .testimonial-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .testimonial-text blockquote {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 30px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .testimonial-text blockquote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 60px;
    color: #1e40af;
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: -30px;
    font-family: serif;
  }
  
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .author-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1e40af;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .testimonial-text blockquote {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .testimonial-text blockquote::before {
      font-size: 40px;
      top: -10px;
      left: -15px;
    }
  }
</style>
